Friday the 13th is considered unlucky for many but matching balls could net a lucky PowerBall player an estimated jackpot of R26.5-million. Battling with January blues? PowerBall might just be the break that you need with its bigger jackpots for 2017 the National Lottery operator said in a statement. To stand a chance of winning this R26.5-million windfall a player will have to match all five winning numbers and the PowerBall and the lucky winner will instantly become PowerBall s first millionaire for 2017. The draw goes out live on e.tv at 9pm and ticket sales close 30 minutes before the draw. PowerBall has created 22 millionaires and more than 34-million winners through all divisions. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share